# Test with windows terminal - cmd - w10 x64 âœ…
# Test with cmd - w10 x64 âœ…
# Test with powershell - w10 x64 âœ…
# Test with github desktop â³ | Read more on: https://github.com/desktop/desktop/issues/10999
